The City shall have the right to shut off/interrupt water service at anytime, without notice, to make repairs,
extensions, or in the case of a fire or any other purpose deemed necessary, or due to nonpayment.
REFUSE AND RECYCLING Please have refuse and recycling containers out at pickup area by
:
6:00 AM on scheduled pickup day. Recyclables should be placed in bright green Kimble recycling
containers, and all trash must be bagged and placed in the dark green Kimble trash container
or use dark bags for items not exceeding 50 pounds to be left outside of the trash container.
DELINQUENT NOTICE A delinquent notice will be mailed to you when payment is not received by 4:30 PM
on the due date. Failure to receive a bill does not waive payment due date or penalty. Water service that
is disconnected due to non-payment will be restored upon receipt of full amount due, including penalties
and fees. Returned payment fee is $30. Otherthan emergency situations, water service will only be turned
on or off during City Hall business hours, which is normally Monday through Friday, 8:00 am - 4:30 pm.
PAYMENT OPTIONS The City of North Canton accepts cash, check, money orders, and credit
cards. Payment can be made online (www.northcantonohio.gov), in person at City hall, or via the
24/7 drop box located at the parking lot entrance to City Hall. Automatic payment may be setup to
allow funds to be deducted from your bank account on or before the monthly due date. Complete,
sign and return this form to the City's Utility Billing Department to sign up for automatic bill payments.
I authorize the City of North Canton to deduct the predetermined payment amount from my listed account on the prede-
termined date, until written notification to cease automatic payment is received. When the due date falls on a weekend
or a holiday, I understand the fund transfer will occur the next business day. I understand that a direct debit returned
unpaid will be assessed a $30 fee. I understand that if at any time I need to make changes to this automatic payment,
I will notify the City of North Canton in writing a minimum of five (5) days prior to the next scheduled funds transfer.
